title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export the data from the table, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should successfully export the data without any exceptions being thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table to the report that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the report. 3. Try to export the data from the table.
